./sdp/verification/t-003@20260408t223256z-verify.md:14:**PASS.** `_invoke_ollama()` performs HTTP POST to `/api/generate` via `urllib.request`. Routing is correct: `get_ollama_route(category)` selects model and port from the dual-socket config in `agent_selector.py`. The `_ollama_base_url()` helper respects `OLLAMA_URL_SOCKET0`/`OLLAMA_URL_SOCKET1` env overrides, falling back to `http://localhost:{port}`. Payload includes `model`, `prompt`, `stream: false`, and tunable options. Response text is extracted from `body["response"]`.
